>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"25596aeb8f5222dcd328b31a398b77a13fdf6d27","tid":2006684,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b2f1740c147484596e95b381669d4eb04fccf6","tid":2006684,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a31fe8f87bc56d69532c100863f67dd55fd0ff","tid":2006684,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25596aeb8f5222dcd328b31a398b77a13fdf6d27","tid":2006684,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b2f1740c147484596e95b381669d4eb04fccf6","tid":2006684,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b11eac40786b62f3d6898883dd6509f0ba6b46","tid":2006684,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138ed9b958fdd0ffa523af40886719f3ceaf992f","tid":2006684,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a31fe8f87bc56d69532c100863f67dd55fd0ff","tid":2006684,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25596aeb8f5222dcd328b31a398b77a13fdf6d27","tid":2006684,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b2f1740c147484596e95b381669d4eb04fccf6